Description: pandoc-latex-french-spaces
        ==========================
        
        `Build
        Status <https://travis-ci.org/chdemko/pandoc-latex-french-spaces/branches>`__
        `Coveralls <https://coveralls.io/github/chdemko/pandoc-latex-french-spaces?branch=0.1.0>`__
