        `PyPI version <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-french-spaces/>`__
        `PyPI
        format <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-french-spaces/0.1.0/>`__
        `License <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chdemko/pandoc-latex-french-spaces/0.1.0/LICENSE>`__
        `Downloads <https://pypi.org/project/pandoc-latex-french-spaces/>`__
